  "about": "Kilowog is a superhero appearing in American comic books published by DC Comics. The character is a member of the Green Lantern Corps.\nKilowog has been substantially adapted into media outside comics, primarily in association with Green Lantern. Michael Clarke Duncan, Kevin Michael Richardson, Dennis Haysbert, and Henry Rollins, among others, have voiced the character in television series and films.",
